-- Congo Republic Says Death Toll From Arms Explosion Rises to 282
-- B y   R o b e r t   M b a k o u
-- 2012-04-02T08:18:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-02/congo-republic-says-death-toll-from-arms-explosion-rises-to-282.html
The Republic of Congo raised the
death toll from a March 4 explosion at an arms depot in the
capital, Brazzaville, to at least 282, Pierre Moussa, the
minister, in charge of probing the accident, said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Mbakou in Brazzaville at 
 rmbakouo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
